textObjects.text: Kang the Conqueror has come! He wants the Earth, and he's got time on his side – but on Earth's side are...the Avengers!

Kang the Conqueror is introduced as "one of the most unique villains of all time!" on this classic cover by Jack Kirby and Dick Ayers.  Unique may be a bit of an understatement, though, as the time-traveling villain is shown standing up to the might of the entire Avengers line-up!
